  .article-container.article-container-wider
    article.group role="article"
        p.govuk-body Here you can download Queen's Awards for Enterprise resources for use in your websites and advertising materials. The Winners' Manual provides more detailed information on where and how you are allowed to use these resources.

        br

        h2.govuk-heading-m Download The Queen's Awards for Enterprise Winners' Manual 2019

        .form-download
          p.govuk-body
            = link_to "Queen's Awards for Enterprise Winners' Manual 2019 (PDF, 1.6MB)",
                      static_s3_asset_path(2019, "Queen's Awards for Enterprise Winners' Manual 2019.pdf"),
                      class: "thumbnail govuk-link",
                      target: "_blank"

        h2.govuk-heading-m Download The Queen's Awards Stakeholders Toolkit 2020

        .form-download
